sources.description:
Tom Benike is the sheriff in a small New Mexico town and best friends with Colin Mandel, a noted hunter who has been featured in several magazines. Diana Kelper works at a local strip joint, The Wild Cherry.  When Diana suddenly disappears, suspicion begins to fall on the strangely absent Colin. In truth, Colin has kidnapped Diana before releasing her into the woods to hunt her down and   kill her. Diana must use intelligence, cunning and animal intuition to avoid becoming Colinâ€™s next trophy.
2007. Stars: Joe Mantegna, Danielle De Luca, Sonja Runar, Ronald Dunas, Arron Shiver
